      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "## Widgets\n1. Total Logs \n 2. Traffic Over Time \n 3. Total Users \n 4. Top Users with Roles \n 5. Top IPs With Failed Login Attempts by User\n 6. Distribution of Events by Name \n 7. Distribution of Events by Component \n 8. Distribution of Events by Login Status \n 9. Distribution of Events by Location \n 10. Event Details",
